desc: I am in my senior year of college in obtaining a bachelors degree in criminal justice.  I do not qualify for financial aid and have used all stafford loans available.  My tuition is approx. $1200 a month and I have 10 courses left which adds up to over $10,000.  I need some assistance to cover my tuition until my graduation date which is August of 2009.
title: Student Loan
